cat("Hello my alien friend! We are carbon-based lives on a planet called\n the Earth, from a distant galaxy called the solar system.\n Who are you? Where are you from?\n It seems that you have the intent to occupy some habitable-zone,\n Earth-like exoplanets. We kindly request you not to do that,\n because we are running out of resources here on Earth,\n and every Earth-like planet is invaluable for us. Thank you!")
